Commissioner McGibbon?

2393
03:31:10,162 --> 03:31:23,171
Before I respond, I'm going to say that just the stretch from Lawrence to the high school does have the separated bike lanes.

2394
03:31:23,691 --> 03:31:27,353
So, you know, the majority of Winthrop Street here is getting that treatment.

2395
03:31:27,414 --> 03:31:29,215
So I'm going to vote yes.

2396
03:31:30,925 --> 03:31:31,645
Commissioner Hunt?

2397
03:31:32,406 --> 03:31:32,706
Yes.

2398
03:31:33,246 --> 03:31:33,886
Chief Buckley?

2399
03:31:34,766 --> 03:31:38,968
Yes, on a vote of three to nothing, the motion is approved.

2400
03:31:39,528 --> 03:31:41,789
I believe that covers the entire plan.

2401
03:31:43,529 --> 03:31:51,032
Can you just actually reiterate that the portion from Lawrence up through the Medford border has actually previously been approved.

2402
03:31:51,772 --> 03:31:57,274
And Todd, the section from Lawrence to the high school includes buffered bike lanes for a lot of it.

2403
03:32:00,550 --> 03:32:01,992
Correct.

2404
03:32:02,392 --> 03:32:19,113
Because most of that stretch from Lawrence Road all the way up to the Winchester line mostly already had no parking, there were some areas that we included parking removal on the opposite side from Victory Park, but that has been previously approved in a previous meeting.

2405
03:32:20,796 --> 03:32:49,533
And I actually just wanted to add that I'm aware, I'm working with staff in our office, there is a path from the Medford High School parking lot down to Victory Park to see what could be involved in marking, making that path better marked so that people could park up at the high school to go to Victory Park and have the shortcut walk down with the handicap parking being the spots on Winthrop by Victory.

2406
03:32:51,755 --> 03:32:54,837
Oh, I just wanted to add that for people who care about that section.

2407
03:32:54,857 --> 03:32:57,579
Okay.

2408
03:32:58,520 --> 03:33:05,845
Um, that concludes the agenda, the table items from the chair.

2409
03:33:05,905 --> 03:33:07,306
This was quite a meeting.

2410
03:33:07,326 --> 03:33:15,913
It was long, but, uh, I'm actually very pleased that the way it was, uh, conducted, uh, well thought out, uh, ideas.

2411
03:33:15,933 --> 03:33:16,013
So.

2412
03:33:23,882 --> 03:33:24,823
