2416
03:33:36,847 --> 03:33:38,227
I couldn't agree more.

2417
03:33:38,247 --> 03:33:39,347
A very well run meeting.

2418
03:33:39,487 --> 03:33:43,708
And I really want to thank everybody for participating and coming and voicing your concerns.

2419
03:33:43,948 --> 03:33:44,888
These are tough decisions.

2420
03:33:45,609 --> 03:33:49,389
